/www.lolaseattle.com/menus/", description: "Lola offers modern, Greek-influenced cuisine with local ingredients. With menu items like salads, kebabs, lamb chops, eggplant, and cod, you’ll enjoy a bit of Greek food with a Pacific Northwest twist. Located in downtown Seattle, Lola restaurant serves a contemporary twist on the classic favorite Greek fare. It’s a lively eatery by Tom Douglas honoring his wife, Jackie’s grandmother Lola who married Louis a Greek immigrant, both full of life. With our menu, we celebrate Louie's Greek spirit and Lola's feistiness. You can find photos of them both on the walls behind Pope's table.", photoCount: "451.0", ratingHistogram: "{\"count1\": 20, \"count2\": 51, \"count3\": 166, \"count4\": 620, \"count5\": 1176}", email: "office@tomdouglas.com", website: "http://www.lolaseattle.com/", rankingPosition: "21.0", hours: "{\"weekRanges\": [[{\"open\": 480, \"openHours\": \"08:00\", \"close\": 840, \"closeHours\": \"14:00\"}, {\"open\": 900, \"openHours\": \"15:00\", \"close\": 1200, \"closeHours\": \"20:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 420, \"openHours\": \"07:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}], [{\"open\": 480, \"openHours\": \"08:00\", \"close\": 840, \"closeHours\": \"14:00\"}, {\"open\": 900, \"openHours\": \"15:00\", \"close\": 1260, \"closeHours\": \"21:00\"}]], \"timezone\": \"America/Los_Angeles\"}", address: "2000 B 4th Ave, Seattle, WA 98121-2415", neighborhoodLocations: "[{\"id\": \"20484040\", \"name\": \"Belltown\"}, {\"id\": \"20933756\", \"name\": \"Downtown\"}]", dishes: ["Crab", "Falafel", "Halloumi", "Burger", "Omelette", "Oyster", "Ribs", "Shawarma", "Shrimp", "Tapa